hma who's now having a flare.","dimension":13,"group":2,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.19024,0.35651,0.072696,0.10539,0.055795,0.06127,0.038442,0.031801,0.026786,0.022954,0.019781,0.01834],"unified_progress":[0.24099,0.16239,0.081064,0.11184,0.076479,0.091089,0.05653,0.049178,0.042266,0.035961,0.029846,0.022369]},{"section":3,"text":"He's using his salbutamol more and the inhaled steroids aren't helping as much.","dimension":10,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.15048,0.25247,0.17333,0.079732,0.063257,0.070725,0.046065,0.058074,0.033027,0.028771,0.023714,0.020358],"unified_progress":[0.12424,0.1712,0.13328,0.093283,0.081797,0.087556,0.064653,0.080751,0.051279,0.044882,0.037713,0.029362]},{"section":4,"text":"The key symptoms here are the recurrent bronchial obstruction, fever, malaise, and those brownish mucous plugs.","dimension":10,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.13572,0.22031,0.1685,0.097306,0.067825,0.071252,0.051591,0.061594,0.040213,0.034206,0.027678,0.023801],"unified_progress":[0.11714,0.15004,0.11795,0.10986,0.084177,0.086764,0.069361,0.078704,0.060117,0.050566,0.04261,0.03271]},{"section":5,"text":"The physical exam shows wheezing but no other abnormalities.","dimension":10,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.11678,0.19485,0.15448,0.099814,0.074586,0.080096,0.059435,0.06687,0.049361,0.041192,0.034597,0.027937],"unified_progress":[0.099785,0.13671,0.11082,0.10714,0.089729,0.091646,0.075323,0.082112,0.067843,0.05699,0.04722,0.03468]},{"section":6,"text":"The CXR has upper lobe infiltrates, which is interesting.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.067388,0.12868,0.12862,0.11404,0.097376,0.090872,0.081068,0.073866,0.074968,0.056043,0.047758,0.039326],"unified_progress":[0.059308,0.099353,0.10461,0.11089,0.10893,0.098908,0.091764,0.083923,0.088691,0.063125,0.050997,0.039496]},{"section":7,"text":"His eosinophil count is really high\u20143000/mL, which is way above nor